data.text: The metrics from the broader market regarding the recovery of meme coins like Shiba Inu (SHIB) and Dogecoin (DOGE) show an interesting twist. Data from the crypto analytics platform IntoTheBlock shows a significant divergence in the whale activities from SHIB and DOGE.
